D&h=88fecfdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=7bfc0958\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[搵工要小心，切勿中美容教育傳銷陷阱]  大學生小心職場陷阱</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164225%2Fpage%2F1&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=71bb531d\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=72aec560\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be83aea2a5a0fda60ba039799a8bf71e264e0cf5","tid":2000004,"uid":169275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2c31208ba5aeec996149f5ff2dae02bedcd72e5","tid":2000004,"uid":67790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7d64ad11fe315743791933e0b3e6c7be4166c45","tid":2000004,"uid":169275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b47f9de718692fc2647490da8907aa856fa21f66","tid":2000004,"uid":67790,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:20:26.000Z","msg":"可以睇定啲先 你可以試下同佢交換contact <br />\nTg 安全啲既， 跟住再睇下佢講既野係點 <br />\n通常真係sales 好快會留出馬腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：我唔係亦絕對唔會做呃人感情同錢既sales"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:28:47.000Z","msg":"個問題佢頭幾個msg已經直接問我電話幾多號 話wtspp我...唔似係因為唔對多用個app咁簡單<br />\n正常唔係傾一段時間都覺得對方係正常同啱傾先換其他contact架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經assume佢係sales"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"咩apps呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:45:28.000Z","msg":"coffee meets bagel"},{"pid":"2d58395d6b401546ec3483d7d565f257d6776f2e","tid":2000004,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7d64ad11fe315743791933e0b3e6c7be4166c45","tid":2000004,"uid":169275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b47f9de718692fc2647490da8907aa856fa21f66","tid":2000004,"uid":67790,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:20:26.000Z","msg":"可以睇定啲先 你可以試下同佢交換contact <br />\nTg 安全啲既， 跟住再睇下佢講既野係點 <br />\n通常真係sales 好快會留出馬腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /